    public class OrthotopePixelModel
extends MBFPixelClassificationModel
    Model of an orthotope/hyperrectangle/box in space. Everything inside classifies as positive, everything outside as negative.

      • OrthotopePixelModel

        public OrthotopePixelModel(float[] minCoords,
                   float[] maxCoords)
        Construct with the given number box. The number of dimensions for each coordinate should be equal to the number of bands in the MBFImages you wish to classify.
        Parameters:
        minCoords - coordinates of the corner of the box with the smallest coordinates.
        maxCoords - coordinates of the corner of the box with the largest coordinates.
